Class ServerMessage

java.lang.Object
  message.MessageProtocol
      message.ServerMessage
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable
public class ServerMessage
extends MessageProtocol

This extends MessageProtocol, providing data useful for a Server to receive. In this message, the server receives a command and a List arguments.

Author:
Michael Tremel (mtremel@email.arizona.edu)
